- Use the module name as prefix and type as suffix (e.g., user.service.ts)
- Example files for User module: user.module.ts, user.resolver.ts, user.service.ts, user.repository.ts, user.schema.ts
- For GraphQL, use *.object.ts for output types and *.input.ts for input types
- If multiple files share the same type, organize them in a dedicated folder (e.g., inputs/)
